Class VerdiPluginClassLoader

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable

    public class VerdiPluginClassLoader
extends org.java.plugin.standard.StandardPluginClassLoader
    Classloader used by Verdi. This extends jpf's StandardPluginClassLoader but overrides getPermissions to return all permissions. This allows jpf to work with webstart.
